text: Rhodora Cadiao is a Filipina politician. She is currently the Governor of Antique Province in Western Visayas Region. As a re-electionist candidate in the May 13, 2019 election under the National Unity Party (Philippines), she defeated Exequiel Javier from Liberal Party. In 2015 Javier was disqualified by the Comelec for suspending his political rival, Valderrama town mayor Joyce Roquero during the election period for the 2013 midterm polls. ==References== * * * * ==External links== *Province of Antique Category:Living people Category:21st-century Filipino women politicians Category:21st-century Filipino politicians Category:Governors of Antique (province) Category:National Unity Party (Philippines) politicians Category:Women provincial governors of the Philippines Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
